which cloud platforms is most secure?

private cloud platform : 

	-  owned & maintained by a single entity 

	-  Single entity has 

			- flexibility of the cloud
			- Security & control of hosting on-premise.

Public/hybrid/internal cloud platforms are not as secure.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

standard cloud service models?

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

   - IaaS : infrastructure-as-a-service [NSSV]

			- Most basic level 

  			- PROVIDER manages :

					1- Networking 
					2- Storage
					3- Servers
					4- Virtualization

			- Main advantage :

 					- USER has a lot of FREEDOM on : 
 							- infrastructure usage (Scalable Storage)
 							- Virtual Machines Managing

 					- Useful for "System Administrators"


			- Examples of IaaS providers include :

					- Amazon Web Services (AWS)
					- Microsoft Azure
					- Google Compute Engine
					- Digital Ocean.

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

	- PaaS : platform-as-a-service [NSSVOMR]

  			- PROVIDER manages :
		
					1- Networking  
					2- Storage
					3- Servers 
					4- Virtualization
	 				5- OS
	 				6- Middleware 
	 				7- Runtime

	
			- USER designs & operates :

					- Data
					- Application
					
			- Useful for Developers		

			Examples of PaaS providers include :

				- AWS Elastic Beanstalk,
				- Windows Azure,
				- Google App Engine,
				- Heroku.

//////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

	- SaaS : software-as-a-service [NSSVOMRDA]

				- Offers the complete package of a web application program

			- PROVIDER manages all system layers :

				1- Networking 
				2- Storage 
				3- Servers 
				4- Virtualization
				5- OS
				6- Middleware
				7- Runtime
				8- Data
				9- Application

			- USER just 
					- sign on
					- use the application ( Gmail, Drive, Office ...)

			- Very Useful for end users

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
